<section>
<title outputclass="splhead-1">General Information</title>

<p>Provides support for interacting with HBASE from Streams. 
</p>
<p>Tuples can be added to HBASE via the HBASEPut operator (including with a checkAndPut condition) or incremented with the HBASEIncrement operator.  Tuples can be retrieved with the HBASEGet operator.  The HBASETableScan operator can output all tuples, or all tuples in a particular row range.  The HBASEDelete operator enables tuples to be delted from HBASE. 
</p>
<p>Configuration uses the same hbase-site.xml that HBASE itself does. 
</p>
